title: Trevor Wallace Roasted Me On Tik Tok!?
description:
I first found out about Trevor (@trevorwallace) when he roasted me online. Today we talk White Claws, dating, sketches, and how to do comedy. Trevor kind of takes charge in interviews me a little bout about Too Hot To Handle! Such a funny episode.
